2009年，胡安·卡納雷（Juan Canale）和同事的[[系統發生學|系統發生學]]研究，將南美洲的食肉牛龍亞科加上肌肉龍，建立成一個食肉牛龍亞科內的次演化支[[短吻龍類|短吻龍類]]（Brachyrostra），定義為：阿貝力龍科中，與食肉牛龍的親緣關係比與[[瑪君龍|瑪君龍]]還要更近的物種；這項分類被許多後來的研究所採納。<ref name="canaleetal2009"/><ref name="delcourt2018"/><ref name="wang2017">{{cite journal | first1 = S. | last1 = Wang | first2 = J. | last2 = Stiegler | first3 = R. | last3 = Amiot | first4 = X. | last4 = Wang | first5 = G.-H. | last5 = Du | first6 = J.M. | last6 = Clark | first7 = X. | last7 = Xu  | title = Extreme ontogenetic changes in a ceratosaurian theropod | journal =  [[Current_Biology|Current Biology]]| volume = 27 | issue = 1 | pages = 144–148 | date = 2017 | doi = 10.1016/j.cub.2016.10.043 | pmid = 28017609 | url = http://www.cell.com/current-biology/pdf/S0960-9822(16)31269-6.pdf}}</ref>其演化樹如下所示：<ref name="canaleetal2009"/>

